The Applied Artificial Intelligence course at 4Geeks Academy is a 6-week program designed for professionals who want to learn and apply AI in their current roles. The course covers various topics such as generative AI, context, prompts, and models. With live online classes, the course accommodates a maximum of 12 participants. Upon completion, students receive an official 4Geeks Completion Certificate. No previous experience is required. For more information, visit the website: [https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course](https://4geeksacademy.com/us/coding-bootcamps/applied-ai-course). stop